e year; ~46% between one and three years; remaining 18% thereafter.\n*   **As of December 31, 2025:** Total backlog was **$28,377 million** (of which $12,116 million was recorded as deferred revenue).\n    *   *Recognition Timeline:* ~32% expected within one year; ~53% in 2027 and 2028; remaining 15% thereafter.\n\n---\n\n### **Customer Concentration Disclosures**\nThe company relies heavily on a single significant customer (Customer A), though the concentration percentage has been gradually decreasing year-over-year. \n\n**Consolidated Revenue from Customer A:**\n*   **2025:** 20.9%\n*   **2024:** 24.2%\n*   **2023:** 25.2%\n\n**Additional Concentration Context:**\n*   Revenue from Customer A relates to **all three** of the company's operating segments.\n*   **No other customers** represented more than 10% of consolidated revenue during the years ended December 31, 2025, 2024, and 2023.",
